file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
    title: Laravel
    description: ''
    version: 1.0.0
servers:
    -
        url: 'http://localhost:8080'
paths:
    /api/login:
        post:
            summary: 顧客担当者ログイン
            description: ''
            parameters:
                -
                    in: header
                    name: Content-Type
                    description: ''
                    example: application/json
                    schema:
                        type: string
                -
                    in: header
                    name: Accept
                    description: ''
                    example: application/json
                    schema:
                        type: string
            responses:
                401:
                    description: ''
                    content:
                        application/json:
                            schema:
                                type: object
                                example:
                                    message: 認証情報が正しくありません
                                properties:
                                    message: { type: string, example: 認証情報が正しくありません }
            tags:
                - Auth
            requestBody:
                required: true
                content:
                    application/json:
                        schema:
                            type: object
                            properties:
                                email:
                                    type: string
                                    description: valueは、有効なメールアドレス形式で指定してください。.
                                    example: arempel@example.org
                                password:
                                    type: string
                                    description: ''
                                    example: cum
                            required:
                                - email
                                - password
            security: []
    /sanctum/csrf-cookie:
        get:
            summary: 'Return an empty response simply to trigger the storage of the CSRF cookie in the browser.'
            description: ''
            parameters:
                -
                    in: header
                    name: Content-Type
                    description: ''
                    example: application/json
                    schema:
                        type: string
                -
                    in: header
                    name: Accept
                    description: ''
                    example: application/json
                    schema:
                        type: string
            responses: {  }
            tags:
                - Endpoints
            security: []
    '/api/users/{user_id}/logout':
        post:
            summary: ''
            description: ''
            parameters:
                -
                    in: header
                    name: Content-Type
                    description: ''
                    example: application/json
                    schema:
                        type: string
                -
                    in: header
                    name: Accept
                    description: ''
                    example: application/json
                    schema:
                        type: string

                    description: ''
